info.name: Sitaphal Ice Cream
info.description: Serves 1 | This blockbuster flavour from Naturals is loved across the nation. This is why we go to great lengths to make this flavour, including sourcing the best Sitaphal from Saswad, Maharashtra. We’ve also innovated and self-engineered the machine used for the pulping of sitaphal. Because we know that you’ll go to great lengths as well to relish this flavour!

info.name: Mango (Medium Fat) Ice Cream
info.description:
Serves 1 | We’ve taken the king of fruits and created an ice cream flavour that rules! Our mango ice cream is made from hand-picked Alphonso mangoes sourced from Ratnagiri. This flavour is every mango lover’s fantasy come true.

Energy (Kcal) :- 149,
Carbohydrate (g):- 17,
Protein (g):- 5,
Fats (g):- 8,
Allergen Declaration:- May contain: Brazilnuts, Cashew, Hazelnuts, Pecans, Pistachio, Walnut, Peanut & Milk,
Serving size : 80 gm per person

info.name: Tender Coconut Ice Cream
info.description: Serves 1 | Naturals is a pioneer of the ‘Tender Coconut’ flavour in the country. As an original flavour from Naturals, it is a huge favourite among ice cream lovers. It’s made with real malai from tender coconuts that are sourced from Kerala and Karnataka.You just can’t have enough of this delicious flavour!

info.name: Chocobite Ice Cream
info.description:
Serves 1 | Have a weakness for chocolate? Then you’ll fall in love with our original Choco Bite ice cream. It’s made from coco mass sourced from Ghana. You’ll even find hand-cut chocolate chunks in this flavour, making it truly hard to resist.

Energy (Kcal) :- 200,
Carbohydrate (g):- 18,
Protein (g):- 6,
Fats (g):- 14,
Allergen Declaration:- May contain: Brazilnuts, Cashew, Hazelnuts, Pecans, Pistachio, Walnut, Peanut & Milk,
Serving size : 80 gm per person

info.name: Orange Pistachio (Medium Fat) Ice Cream
info.description:
Serves 1 | Orange Pistachio is inspired by the nostalgic taste of orange barfi which is loved by all. This flavour also has a Turkish influence, since orange and pista is a combination used for making Turkish delights. Naturals has launched the Orange Pistachio ice cream, which has an international yet desi twist. Pulpy, zesty orange bites compliment the nutty, roasted pistachios in this unique flavour!
